# Dependencies
node_modules/
# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
# Environment (safe to include even if unused)
.env
.env.*.local
# OS/editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
Third-party packages installed by npm in your future pracs. Large and rebuildable.
Commiting it bloats the repo and causes merge pain.
Runtime and crash logs. Useful locally only. Not source code. Regenerated on each
run.
.DS_Store
macOS Finder metadata. Machine-specific clutter. Safe to ignore.
Thumbs.db
Windows Explorer cache. Machine-specific. Safe to ignore.
.vscode/
Editor settings and local extensions. Personal configuration. Avoids editor-specific
noise.
Environment variables: DB URI, secrets, ports. Must not be
public.
